Usage: kelly_criterion --p <PROBABILITY_INCREASE> --l <FRACTION_LOSS> --g <FRACTION_GAIN> --assets <ASSETS>

Options:
-p, --p <PROBABILITY_INCREASE> Probability that the investment increases in value (0 <= p <= 1)
-l, --l <FRACTION_LOSS> Fraction that is lost in a negative outcome (e.g., 0.1 for 10% loss)
-g, --g <FRACTION_GAIN> Fraction that is gained in a positive outcome (e.g., 0.1 for 10% gain)
-a, --assets <ASSETS> Current assets
-h, --help Print help
